# [MPLS](../wg/mpls.html)

## Summary

The MPLS Working Group met at IETF 126. The session covered administration updates, errata reviews, and status reports, followed by eight technical presentations focusing on MPLS Network Actions (MNA) for OAM, Deterministic Networking (DetNet), Explicit Congestion Notification (ECCN), In-situ OAM (IOAM), and RSVP-TE extensions. Key highlights included discussions on MNA capability discovery mechanisms, carrying ECN within MNA, and utilizing Segment Routing (SR) adjacency sets for RSVP-TE tunnels.

